# Homework 1 - NDC to RGB Shader
John Salame
CSCI 5239 Spring 2023

Based on ex01 silly shader by
Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder
CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2023

### Description
Demonstrates use of vertex and fragment shaders.
The color of each fragment depends on the position on the screen in Normalized Device Coordinates.
Red intensity increases rightward.
Green intensity increases upward.
Blue intensity increases if the object is close to the camera.

The bottom left corner should be dark, with some blue.
The top left corner should be cyan.
The top right corner should be yellow or white.
The bottom right corner should be purple / magenta.


### Key bindings
  0-4        Change location of object to center or corners of screen
  m          Toggle shader
  o          Change objects
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  ] and [    Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
